replicas                 ➔ Number of Pods to run
selector                 ➔ Tells ReplicaSet/Deployment which Pods it controls (by matching labels)
template                 ➔ Describes the Pods to create
template.metadata.labels ➔ Labels that will be attached to the Pods
template.spec            ➔ The spec for the Pod, like what container(s) to run
containers               ➔ List of containers to run in each Pod
image                    ➔ Docker image to use for the container

Example YAML file :

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: ReplicaSet
metadata:
  name: replica01
  labels:
    type: frontend
  namespace: nisha
spec:
  replicas: 3
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      type: php
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
       type: php
    spec:
      containers:
       - name: phpcontainer
         image: phpimg
